1-0, with some modifications made to the following functions, in order to support cell-data as input:

dss_core_defl.m
dss_core_pca.m
dss_core_symm.m
dss_preprocess.m
dss_sphere.m
pre_sphere.m

Also, it has a denoise_avg2 added, which specifically allows for epoch-boundary respecting averaging, cell-input, and specific baseline options
